{"tid":2048943,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要分手","createTime":"2020-06-03T06:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T08:28:29.000Z","uid":232239,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3575d7dc745eccaeea5b06111fa30ab9450cc186","tid":2048943,"uid":232239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左兩年幾 前幾日佢同我講分手<br />\n佢覺得同我一齊好大壓力 因為我成日咩都管住佢 又係咁chur住佢話要見<br />\n再加埋之前我搵過佢fd討論有關佢既野 希望知道佢諗d咩<br />\n佢覺得咁樣好唔尊重佢 但我只係想搵個了解佢既人知道佢諗咩 其他事根本唔會搵佢<br />\n好想救番段關係 我可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656fdbe1196aac8ce45409de81e3e290d6f10f5b","tid":2048943,"uid":218575,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"唔好挽 同我一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59566512870f98a06770aa66de13b9510e02f531","tid":2048943,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:28:04.000Z","msg":"兩年幾先有呢個問題？咁之前係點相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8605dcda608244050bb9c0cfca73c87c78afb437","tid":2048943,"uid":211729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3575d7dc745eccaeea5b06111fa30ab9450cc186","tid":2048943,"uid":232239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:25:52.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左兩年幾 前幾日佢同我講分手<br />\n佢覺得同我一齊好大壓力 因為我成日咩都管住佢 又係咁chur住佢話要見<br />\n再加埋之前我搵過佢fd討論有關佢既野 希望知道佢諗d咩<br />\n佢覺得咁樣好唔尊重佢 但我只係想搵個了解佢既人知道佢諗咩 其他事根本唔會搵佢<br />\n好想救番段關係 我可以點做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:29:13.000Z","msg":"反而我like 呢種"},{"pid":"85b6667d347c93fd7eacbb1ca01a62a1cdf3cf6d","tid":2048943,"uid":334292,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T06:29:38.000Z","msg":"佢仲愛你嘅話呢啲都唔係問題，藉口黎"},{"pid":"be93ceb66597bf